OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and sunny, and becoming
OL,6,Fvery hot, locally exceptionally hot
OL,7,Ftoday, with the potential for
OL,8,Ftemperatures to cause significant
OL,9,Fdisruption. Also feeling humid with
OL,10,Fonly light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDespite largely clear skies
OL,13,Fmany places will have another warm or
OL,14,Fvery warm night, especially in large
OL,15,Ftowns and cities where an
OL,16,Fexceptionally warm night is possible.
OL,17,FRemaining humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
