OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FSunny and generally very
OL,6,Fhot, locally exceptionally hot across
OL,7,Fwestern areas. The east or southeast
OL,8,Fbreeze will keep many coastal areas
OL,9,Fcooler than inland.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHot or
OL,12,Fvery hot Friday, thereafter
OL,13,Ftemperatures decreasing. Bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells Friday and Saturday,
OL,15,Fchance of thunderstorms, mainly
OL,16,FSaturday night. Cloudier Sunday,
OL,17,Fpatchy light rain possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
